{
  "stem": "1873.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 411.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When the [INAUDIBLE] in that part of the camp, we were 500 at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If there were 500 people, I guarantee about 450 stand in the line for food, not knowing that practically 95% of the Germans  are killed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But now, I'm told.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One told another one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And simple-- and they're kissing each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember, an older man-- I say, older.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe he was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His daughter was 17.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe he was 50 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a tailor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was, I remember, walking back and forth and holding his hand and breaking his fingers, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why do we need it  for?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We could live another two weeks, another three weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why do  we need  it for?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, when you're close to die, every second is precious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't imagine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had never the feeling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You will never understand it, even.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so, I remember this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember people-- talking about heroism.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Told you about the people picking up the-- [INAUDIBLE] the money pieces.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember people going back to the barracks, putting-- picking up the prayer shawls, which they hide, under the threat of death, taking them out, putting on the head, and praying.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They decide not to escape, because they realized theirs no salvation outside, either.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Their families were killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't commit suicide, probably, because the Jewish religion forbids-- forbids suicides.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they didn't want to live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they put on the prayer shawls and started to pray, the last minute, facing the  Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And probably, when the Germans surrounded them, they were praying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were defying them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That we are still Jews and believe  in our God.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] I think, something like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a lot of heroism going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
